Mothers Day For Wonderful Partner Vase of Flowers Card

Review Mothers Day For Wonderful Partner Vase of Flowers Card – Mothers Day Cards This item is trending! Mothers Day For Wonderful Partner Vase of Flowers Card help you save during this period Mothers Day For Wonderful Partner Vase of Flowers Card There are many featuresThis pretty, contemporary floral Mother’s Day greeting card for your partner features a bouquet of pink, blue and white flowers in a pale blue vase on a dark blue background. The greeting on the front cover is, ‘To my wonderful Partner’!’ in white handwriting script at the top. Below the vase of flowers, it says, ‘With lots of love on ‘ and then ‘MOTHER’S DAY!’ in a decorative lettering. The inside message is just a suggestion and you can easily change it or delete it altogether if you prefer a ‘blank inside’ card. Price:$4.42
